{"tid":1313423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，無腦盲撐嘅人真喺好可怕，情願你喺港豬都唔撚好盲撐","createTime":"2019-07-13T18:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:59:13.000Z","uid":85554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05892c698079feaeec1ed78bfb6d93c95e39f46f","tid":1313423,"uid":85554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:20:14.000Z","msg":"曾經所謂同學，用下你個死人豬腦好無？今時今日咁嘅局面喺林奠 政府搞出來，警察選擇維護呢個醜惡政權，與市民為敵，請問聲佢地邊忽辛苦？口口聲聲話人喺暴徒，有邊次唔喺警察追住示威者來打？成日屌鳩大陸人水貨客阻住晒，宜家有班人肯行出來去幫你解決問題你竟然話人喺暴徒，咁你唔打開你屋企門口邀請水貨客大媽上你屋企happy gathering <br />\n<br />\n仲好意思鬧人「偽香港人」，你又為呢個家做過啲乜嘢，大家上下齊心遊行抗議個陣你咪旅行打卡囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港就喺俾你呢啲藍絲 廢老 無腦廢搞拖垮晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V91v1ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV91v1ab.png&h=b0fae2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUZmoox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUZmoox.png&h=5db560a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d79NiWT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd79NiWT.png&h=204b97c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxmDqBU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxmDqBU.png&h=d23668a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95b6711fd10bf83af014b42566f8db7156fd8c39","tid":1313423,"uid":68483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:35:06.000Z","msg":"醜人多百怪"},{"pid":"e6b4dd09adb6ca6766763d89964d2a7377658d65","tid":1313423,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/香港網民常用政治詞彙\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%A9%9E%E5%BD%99&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=2d624a8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wik